To use catch and exceptions.

First I created the Usuario class in the file Usuario.php
    In this class i added to the setCorreo function a filter using the
    FILTER_VALIDATE_EMAIL function already part of PHP to check if the email 
    is in a valid format.
Then i created the Alumno and Admin classes, both refered the Usuario class.
And finally on the index.php file I instanced bothe Alumno and Admin, and made an example of the catch function.

To see the output I used the terminal to cd into the folder where these project its and then used: 
    php -S localhost:8000
After that i used http://localhost:8000/index.php on my browser to check the output.